HOVE Risk-Control Linker is a public model release package for severe-error
and high-distance false-positive risk control in clinical concept linking.

Repository code, documentation, tests, release scripts, and public aggregate
metadata are distributed under the MIT License:
- https://opensource.org/license/mit
